Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Penguin_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Penguin_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Penguin_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.61,0:23:16.86,Penguin_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ここは　どこ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.50,0:23:22.24,Penguin_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どうして 僕はこんなところにいるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.51,0:23:28.67,Penguin_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕たちはすべてを失った
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.69,0:23:30.70,Penguin_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,それでもお前は続けるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.03,0:23:34.04,Penguin_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,許さないぞ　決着をつけよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.05,0:23:39.29,Penguin_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生存戦略　私を放さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Penguin_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.05,0:00:29.65,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.65,0:00:32.36,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不巧 怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.77,0:00:35.48,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可疑  很显然有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.60,0:00:38.94,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要留个言啊 那在这儿写
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.02,0:00:40.17,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿什么写
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.17,0:00:41.40,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边那两个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.61,0:00:45.58,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼鬼祟祟地蹲在人家门前干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.87,0:00:47.36,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可不是坏人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.36,0:00:48.98,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 有点事…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.98,0:00:51.67,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是有东西想送给阳毬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.91,0:02:33.00,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是double H… 本尊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.12,0:02:37.38,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是来见阳毬的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.43,0:02:40.30,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们和阳毬是小学同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.62,0:02:44.02,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是阳毬织好了送给我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.29,0:02:46.18,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她总说 我有一直支持你们哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.26,0:02:48.39,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们的羁绊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.99,0:02:52.10,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 无论如何也想和她见上一面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.10,0:02:54.27,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟她当面道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.65,0:02:56.19,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.50,0:02:59.53,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 阳毬出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.53,0:03:01.84,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天应该回来不了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.19,0:03:03.92,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.92,0:03:05.06,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.14,0:03:09.46,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那请把这个转交给她 这是我们的新专辑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.39,0:03:12.48,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要让她先听听 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.93,0:03:15.72,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我一定转交给她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.36,0:03:26.52,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶马
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.97,0:03:29.18,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荻野目
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.31,0:03:33.51,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚又去了一趟警察局
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.12,0:03:36.11,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们说没有什么消息
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.34,0:03:37.30,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.92,0:03:42.26,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳毬到底为什么没去叔叔家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:51.31,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我傻 要是能多站在阳毬的角度上想想的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:57.77,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想 阳毬应该跟冠叶在一起的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:04.33,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实行之日终于到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.05,0:04:07.95,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在每个箱子里都放进50个泰迪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.40,0:04:10.73,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他路线的量准备好了没
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.73,0:04:13.63,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在生产当中 一切顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.14,0:04:16.08,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还需要300个才够
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.18,0:04:17.64,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要赶上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.68,0:04:19.87,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到 这就去森林
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.87,0:04:22.05,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.56,0:04:24.00,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下 大事不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.00,0:04:25.02,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.17,0:04:28.37,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,rolling的生产基地 似乎已经暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.75,0:04:32.34,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里还有我们本次计划的一部分数据
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.55,0:04:34.57,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不将它们销毁的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:37.66,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好 这事由我来处理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.20,0:04:41.90,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那药已经不起作用了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.70,0:04:50.44,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.13,0:04:50.22,Penguin_disclaimer,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真俐所告知的难以置信的话 我只是想救阳毬而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.13,0:04:50.22,Penguin_disclaimer,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天晚上\N东鸥医院诊察室
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.13,0:04:50.22,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.13,0:04:50.22,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.44,0:04:53.31,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑 到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.31,0:04:57.91,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的药 会随着使用次数的增加 药效逐渐下降
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.04,0:05:01.25,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的情况 你应该听说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.37,0:05:03.61,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 阳毬会怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.87,0:05:05.03,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:07.97,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魂淡 我杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.76,0:05:17.88,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.31,0:05:21.58,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你杀不了我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.02,0:05:23.39,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 你不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.78,0:05:28.26,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一个办法 可以救你妹妹的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.87,0:05:35.28,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要乖乖听从我们的诅咒就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.18,0:05:52.31,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小冠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:53.92,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:56.28,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 就是想抱抱你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.72,0:06:03.20,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会一直在一起的 小冠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.05,0:06:05.33,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:13.81,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经明白 我不用再害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.46,0:06:16.66,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你告诉我这一切的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.29,0:06:19.46,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.77,0:06:23.35,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 已经足够
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.61,0:06:28.03,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 一直以来让你活在痛苦当中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.72,0:06:30.38,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我心甘情愿的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:34.71,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是我装着恍若未见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.42,0:06:39.87,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装作没看见 为了我 小冠你牺牲了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.16,0:06:41.79,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至是你的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.85,0:06:45.52,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳毬 你还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.09,0:06:48.75,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们成为家人的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.30,0:06:50.58,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:55.26,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时 你给我的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:59.47,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你… 我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.51,0:07:02.41,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.68,0:07:08.19,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会救你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.37,0:07:12.46,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.74,0:07:16.60,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小冠 别去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.24,0:07:19.31,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要去做那些危险的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.39,0:07:27.99,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是让我现在死 我也无怨言
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.75,0:07:36.79,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你要是死了 我绝不会原谅这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.88,0:07:40.40,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会把这世界燃成灰烬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.52,0:07:47.54,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去去就来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:54.28,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳毬 你就是我的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.68,0:08:15.67,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.43,0:08:21.88,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小冠 等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:37.25,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.25,0:08:40.02,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看 企鹅们游泳好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.02,0:08:41.16,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.07,0:08:46.23,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.85,0:08:52.07,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 要是那天 那时
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.58,0:08:55.01,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就那样死去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.25,0:08:58.13,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小冠就不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.95,0:09:09.98,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神啊 我求求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.61,0:09:12.87,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请将因为我的视而不见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:17.64,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而从小冠那里夺走的东西还给他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:21.44,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您一定要救救他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.09,0:09:25.15,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会将从他那里得到的东西全部交还的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.65,0:09:28.21,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括我的生命 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.50,0:10:01.07,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是对不起 突然叫你出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.26,0:10:05.59,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 不过发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:12.55,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.15,0:10:13.81,Penguin_disclaimer,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然间转向我的刀刃 我根本没想过当时它会朝我刺来 没想到事情 会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.15,0:10:13.81,Penguin_disclaimer,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复仇结束的那个晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.15,0:10:13.81,Penguin_disclaimer,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉面屋 店内
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.33,0:10:17.38,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.76,0:10:21.90,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蕗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.85,0:10:31.03,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蕗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.82,0:10:37.51,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.55,0:10:40.78,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全…全都是你不好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.01,0:10:44.30,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是爱与罪的巴洛克
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.46,0:10:47.00,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上叫救护车…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:50.76,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合 我终于明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.25,0:11:02.24,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合 我终于明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.73,0:11:03.83,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.70,0:11:08.78,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了为什么只有我们俩留在了这个世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.36,0:11:11.54,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.56,0:11:16.60,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你我都是从一开始就迷失了的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.13,0:11:22.15,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 世上大部分的孩子和我们是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.75,0:11:26.25,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 哪怕一次也好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:34.23,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要有人对我们说 我爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.06,0:11:46.66,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察已经发现了你们的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.80,0:11:50.98,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连现在他们也在监视着你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.99,0:11:57.91,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要回头就只有趁现在了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.78,0:12:01.16,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要完成计划
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.16,0:12:03.09,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救阳毬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.60,0:12:08.73,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.75,0:12:12.51,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的跟踪车辆正在转盘处监视着你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.61,0:12:14.77,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 交给我处理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:19.20,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.97,0:12:35.09,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁快帮忙叫警察来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.09,0:12:36.07,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.07,0:12:38.24,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 我怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.30,0:12:40.46,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  很危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.64,0:12:42.72,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.91,0:13:02.99,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.99,0:13:03.53,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.53,0:13:05.16,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都爆炸了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.94,0:13:08.17,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好狠…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.93,0:13:13.71,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手 他们只是在利用你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.96,0:13:15.88,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 还不止这些
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.93,0:13:18.45,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经知道他的真实身份了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.68,0:13:22.74,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他只是个诅咒 不是存在于这世上的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.05,0:13:24.17,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:44.15,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经被包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.83,0:13:46.66,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃无谓的抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.66,0:13:47.92,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽快投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.18,0:13:49.23,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再重复一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.46,0:13:51.27,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经被包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.89,0:13:53.58,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃无谓的抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.58,0:13:54.97,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽快投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.56,0:13:58.40,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冠叶 投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.93,0:14:01.36,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 我会跟你一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.61,0:14:03.32,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.75,0:14:12.05,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要跟着我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.52,0:14:13.66,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.21,0:14:16.20,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这条街的地下是一个迷宫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.74,0:14:18.23,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有任何记载
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.23,0:14:22.32,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多地方已多年无人涉足
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:26.18,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们用的 就是其中一个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.63,0:14:28.88,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁也不会找到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.62,0:14:30.63,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.51,0:14:33.86,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要拯救阳毬的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.67,0:14:36.05,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.43,0:14:42.42,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她和你只是毫无关系的外人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.95,0:14:50.47,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳毬是我的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.28,0:14:55.11,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看着我 我才是你的妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.89,0:15:00.75,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快醒醒吧 我们是被过去诅咒的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.13,0:15:04.96,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的父亲犯下多么不可饶恕的罪过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.01,0:15:07.23,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也该知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.07,0:15:12.77,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 他们利用完之后就抛弃了我们的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.79,0:15:18.88,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要再跟着我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.83,0:15:26.99,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 我不会让你去的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.68,0:15:33.02,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那天起 我就一直在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.53,0:15:35.72,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不再被剥夺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.06,0:15:37.73,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不再失去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.38,0:15:43.76,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在去的话 肯定也会被抛弃的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.01,0:15:45.74,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定会被杀掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.87,0:15:47.88,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.88,0:15:52.13,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 我不要再次失去你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.83,0:15:59.11,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 对我说声
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.62,0:16:03.02,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我 我是你心爱的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.53,0:16:06.93,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像从前那样 一次就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.43,0:16:09.17,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.41,0:16:12.70,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算和你一起承受永世的诅咒  也心甘情愿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.44,0:16:15.55,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真砂子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.29,0:16:24.81,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经逃不了了 快投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.24,0:16:27.70,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经被包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.15,0:16:31.26,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止无谓的反抗 投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.15,0:16:32.44,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.44,0:16:33.99,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再重复一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.51,0:16:36.95,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经被包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.42,0:16:40.67,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止无谓的反抗 投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.50,0:16:43.13,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经无路可逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.03,0:17:08.40,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样 就没有碍眼的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:10.84,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冠叶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.95,0:17:22.96,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.77,0:17:46.52,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真砂子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.77,0:17:50.86,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.70,0:17:55.16,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:18:01.32,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要放开我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.33,0:18:16.12,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.02,0:18:15.94,Penguin_disclaimer,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和冠叶分别的日子 哥哥为了将一切留给我和万里夫 抛弃了夏芽家 抛弃了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.02,0:18:15.94,Penguin_disclaimer,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10年前\N公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.02,0:18:15.94,Penguin_disclaimer,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.02,0:18:15.94,Penguin_disclaimer,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.50,0:18:20.04,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把真砂子和万里夫留在我的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.39,0:18:22.12,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们一直留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.85,0:18:26.06,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲 我会留在这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.86,0:18:29.48,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 真砂子和万里夫…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.48,0:18:31.48,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您把他们送回夏芽家去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.71,0:18:33.47,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们做个普通的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:41.33,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 你不可以这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.36,0:18:46.61,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要离开我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.31,0:19:09.74,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冠叶 冠叶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.70,0:19:19.53,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高仓冠叶 你已经无路可逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.91,0:19:21.73,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快停止无谓的反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.26,0:19:23.25,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.76,0:19:26.17,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高仓冠叶 你已经无路可逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.56,0:19:28.53,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}不要做无谓的反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.48,0:19:30.58,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙啊 我们被包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.05,0:19:32.19,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.44,0:19:35.56,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样下去 我们都会死在这里 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.23,0:19:38.47,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你们了 快投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.74,0:19:42.57,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的 他们是不会放过我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.10,0:19:45.24,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去就只有死路一条
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.47,0:19:46.77,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.85,0:19:56.31,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等你们30秒 请在这之前投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.59,0:20:00.12,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万里夫 我对不起你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.91,0:20:02.87,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没能救你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.84,0:20:12.14,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好 就我来做诱饵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.89,0:20:15.39,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们趁机带着冠叶离开…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.79,0:20:25.91,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏芽家的诅咒 祖父的诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.18,0:20:29.39,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能从这个世界手中得到成熟果实的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.39,0:20:31.99,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有那些贪得无厌的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.44,0:20:38.14,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 舍弃一切的父亲 在我看来是那么的美
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.84,0:20:43.60,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 眼中所看到的美 都会有阴影
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.09,0:20:46.33,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里是美丽的棺材
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.67,0:20:49.75,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾经只是个没有察觉这一切的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.82,0:20:54.31,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冠叶 是你 将我和万里夫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.35,0:20:56.75,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那片阴影中救出
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.23,0:20:58.88,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来到这个能够看见光明的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.18,0:21:05.75,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次 轮到我了 我不会让你葬送在这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.86,0:21:14.69,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了了 我要摧毁…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.89,0:21:28.27,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝美之棺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.69,0:23:07.22,Penguin_disclaimer,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我孤身一人 不知道发生了什么 不知道为何自己身处此地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.69,0:23:07.22,Penguin_disclaimer,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箱子中\N十年前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.61,0:23:16.86,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是… 什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.50,0:23:22.24,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.51,0:23:28.67,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们失去了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.69,0:23:30.70,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你还是会执迷不悟 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.03,0:23:34.04,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会原谅你的 我们做个了断吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.05,0:23:39.29,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生存战略 不要离开我
