Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.18,0:01:04.74,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸出的手划过又落下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.14,0:01:08.39,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法交错的幻觉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.26,0:01:11.99,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旋转木马在空中旋转
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.99,0:01:15.50,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗的帷幕徐徐落下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.89,0:01:19.60,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密揭晓的神圣之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.77,0:01:24.67,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深夜开窗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.08,0:01:30.09,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召唤秘密的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.32,0:01:35.58,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掀起深红的窗帘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.83,0:01:39.70,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐去微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.72,0:01:43.81,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年啊 回归自我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.98,0:01:46.50,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘上特快列车
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.55,0:01:49.23,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带我去梦幻之岛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.23,0:01:54.42,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺取一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.42,0:01:57.44,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使被指指点点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.44,0:02:00.69,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以立刻逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.85,0:02:06.78,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要一切中意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.46,0:02:13.30,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年少女结成圆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.30,0:02:16.76,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸出的手划过又落下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.21,0:02:19.96,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轮回的命运
